Package: eribayes
Title: Tools to simplify Bayesian model fitting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Shafer", , "tom.shafer@elderresearch.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Elder Research", , , "support@elderresearch.com", "cph"))
Description: |-
  The package *eribayes* supports Bayesian model fitting and
  workflow by providing wrappers for common needs that are
  compatible with multiple MCMC frontends for the Stan
  probabilistic programming language.
